{"tid":1578901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那國家網信辦：Facebook及Twitter內容審核比中方更有招數","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T11:04:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"92ad28eab5d033288f9ef3eec37f9fd1d6c6336b","tid":1578901,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"在北京，國家互聯網信息辦公室副主任劉烈宏批評，社交網站Facebook、Twitter等以散佈假新聞為藉口，封禁一批發布客觀理性聲音的中國賬戶，但與此同時大量歪曲事實、攻擊抹黑中國的謠言信息卻大行其道，充分表明有關公司在內容審核上更有招數及非常精準，認為如果要取經，找他們可能更合適。"},{"pid":"234343827a374d5782cc4524912970d90610a5c4","tid":1578901,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1173772&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1173772%26csid%3D261_341&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4e955084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1173772&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ce9ecc6a2cc87e8639adf5f5207f55a8226c92ab","tid":1578901,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:31:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32577ebdbd8ac7f5e4dae75eec3f80ced80bec7d","tid":1578901,"uid